WEBVTT

00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:01.976
We need balance,

00:04:02.000 --> 00:04:06.136
and the only way things will change
is if we take a real honest look

00:04:06.160 --> 00:04:08.376
at the scripts that have been
passed down to us

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:10.216
from generation to generation

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:13.456
and the roles that,
as men, we choose to take on

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:14.760
in our everyday lives.

00:04:15.320 --> 00:04:16.576
So speaking of scripts,

00:04:16.600 --> 00:04:19.560
the first script I ever got
came from my dad.

00:04:20.079 --> 00:04:21.279
My dad is awesome.

00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:27.960
He's loving, he's kind,
he's sensitive, he's nurturing,

00:04:28.800 --> 00:04:30.016
he's here.